data.description: Welcome to 537 Clinton Dr, Temple, GA 30179 - a modern and luxurious home spanning over 2500 square feet.  Inside, you'll find an open kitchen with custom-built White and Graphite cabinets, Iced White Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious breakfast area. The dining room features faux wood beams for a touch of elegance.  Upstairs, four spacious bedrooms offer walk-in closets. The master suite boasts an oversized closet, tile flooring, a walk-in shower, soaking tub, and a double vanity.  Step outside to the covered back porch and a fenced-in yard for entertaining and play.  Contact us today to secure your dream home!
